      <title>欧洲第三季度中期业绩：投资者对业绩表现感到满意，但对中国市场感到担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/q3-half-time-europe-investors-reward-beats-fret-about-china-2024-11-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲第三季度的企业盈利大多超出了市场的低预期，尽管中国需求疲软值得谨慎，但投资者对超出预期的收益的回报比过去几年都要丰厚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/q3-half-time-europe-investors-reward-beats-fret-about-china-2024-11-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 06:15:36 GMT</pubDate>
